      .container
        .row.boxes
          .col-sm-1-3.text-center
            h1 Secured
            p Completely safe and secure, our drivers make your safety their priority.

          .col-sm-1-3.text-center
            h1 Chauffeured
            p You call us, we pick you up and take you wherever you want to go.

          .col-sm-1-3.text-center
            h1 Luxurious
            p Take a ride with us, experience nightlife like it should be.


    section.call-cta-container
      .container
        .row
          .col-sm-1.text-center
            a(href="tel:19316458140")
              button.btn.btn-lg.btn-cta +1 931 645 8140

        .row
          .text-center
            p Call for rates and availability

    footer
      .container
        .row
          p Made by us
